story.storyDescription: He's coming for Tasha...she just doesn't know it yet.
story.title: Lights Please - Part 1

messages.text: um…mom did you forget to pay the energy bill??
whatever. did you or did you not??
Weird. I’m sure its just a power outage or something.
I don’t know. Could be anything.
i just dont like being home alone
I’ll be home within the hour.
and you’re sure you paid the energy??
What, you think some ghost is behind this?
Well, this is real life. Nothing is gonna’ happen to you.
Are you too much of a scardy cat?
house is creepy when its dark
Anything is creepy when dark. But I bet you’re the safest there.
You live there. Feel most comfortable there.
So the lights cut. Big deal.
idk just this feeling in my gut
You’re cute sometimes, you know that.
i dont like how youre taking this as a joke
Breathe. I’ll be there in just a few.
Tasha, what has gotten into you?
You need to seriously calm down.
someone is in here with me
What makes you think there is someone in there?
i can hear them creeping around
trying to make it to my room
And you’re confident someone is there?
You’re sure you’re not just hearing things?
I need to know for sure.
how can you not believe me????
i hear him opening drawers in the kitchen
Then how’d you know it was a he?
Calm down. Can you get a visual?
I need to know for sure someone is there.
i can hear them plain as day!!!!!!!!
I’m about to call the cops. So this better be real.
fine fine, i freakin look, happy
bet i die in the process
idk im not in his head
big he or SHE for all i know
i heard him pull a knife from the sheath on the counter
do you think he knows im here
Stay hidden and hold on, I’m contacting the cops.
Does he know where you are?
idk, he is just walking around saying it
im at the bottom of the stairs
Keep me updated if you can.
You’ll be saved in just a minute.
Are you safe?! Have you moved?!
The police are on their way.
Who is this?!? Do you have my daughter???!!
I swear if you lay a finger on her…
Sorry Carol. I’m taking her with me. Like it should’ve been.
YOU WILL NOT GET AWAY WITH THIS!
Click below to see what happens next...
